                                        <span class="f-title"><i class="fa fa-birthday-cake"></i> Birthday:</span>
                                        <p>
                                            December 17, 1985
                                        </p>
                                        <span class="f-title"><i class="fa fa-phone"></i> Phone Number:</span>
                                        <p>
                                            +1-989-232435234
                                        </p>
                                        <span class="f-title"><i class="fa fa-medkit"></i> Blood group:</span>
                                        <p>
                                            B+
